translate indonesian ep2_18_end_1f348dc9:
    # "Well, where've you been?"
    "Nah, kau dari mana saja?"

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_24a0d067:
    # mc "Hey, hey, what's with the tone?"
    mc "Hei, hei, nada bicaramu kenapa?"

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_f712d0c3:
    # mc "I was just taking a walk."
    mc "Aku hanya jalan-jalan."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_c9786058:
    # "Do you realise that if you get into trouble again, there's nothing we can do. You'll go to jail!"
    "Apa kau sadar kalau kau mendapat masalah lagi, tidak ada yang bisa kami lakukan. Kau akan masuk penjara!"

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_e6902fd9:
    # mc "Look, Mary, if you want me to tell you the truth, you have to learn to trust me!"
    mc "Dengar, Mary, kalau kau ingin aku mengatakan yang sebenarnya, kau harus belajar mempercayaiku!"

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_553a4b89:
    # "That's hard to do when your friend is constantly involved in murky stories."
    "Itu sulit dilakukan kalau temanmu terus terlibat dalam cerita-cerita mencurigakan."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_9326340e:
    # mc "I was just taking a walk. Trust me."
    mc "Aku hanya jalan-jalan. Percayalah padaku."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_b554310f:
    # "And you're not doing any shady business anymore?"
    "Dan kau tidak melakukan bisnis gelap lagi?"

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_2445cab2:
    # mc "No."
    mc "Tidak."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_28b441b3:
    # "…."
    "...."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_b7fcfb8d:
    # "Very well. I trust you."
    "Baiklah. Aku percaya padamu."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_994d8683:
    # "But only for the last time."
    "Tapi hanya untuk terakhir kalinya."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_1df3044f:
    # mc "Thanks"
    mc "Terima kasih"

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_3aa32864:
    # "Good night."
    "Selamat malam."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_248ed6b8:
    # mc "Yes, I lied to her again. However, what choice did I have?"
    mc "Ya, aku berbohong padanya lagi. Tapi pilihan apa yang kupunya?"

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_d4970b75:
    # mc "Should I have told her that I owe a lot of money to gangsters? That any day now I could be slaughtered for unpaid interest? Or that I went to get a gun for self-defence?"
    mc "Haruskah aku memberitahunya bahwa aku berutang banyak uang pada gangster? Bahwa kapan saja aku bisa dibantai karena bunga yang belum dibayar? Atau bahwa aku pergi mengambil pistol untuk membela diri?"

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_f467a753:
    # mc "…."
    mc "...."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_98842f4e:
    # mc "Any day could be my last day."
    mc "Hari apa pun bisa menjadi hari terakhirku."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_3bf4708c:
    # mc "And if I'm destined to die in a gunfight, I want the rest of my life to be with the person I love most in the world...."
    mc "Dan kalau aku memang ditakdirkan mati dalam baku tembak, aku ingin sisa hidupku bersama orang yang paling kucintai di dunia...."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_c9dacd23:
    # mc "Mary."
    mc "Mary."

translate indonesian ep2_18_end_fff5ce9e:
    # mc "I'll need to buy her favourite red wine and find a suitable film to watch in a romantic setting. A CD with a suitable film can be found in the hall."
    mc "Aku perlu membeli anggur merah favoritnya dan mencari film yang cocok untuk ditonton dalam suasana romantis. CD berisi film yang cocok bisa ditemukan di ruang tamu."

translate indonesian strings:
    old "Требование: Привязанность Марины (3)"
    new "Syarat: Afeksi Mary (3)"
